data.description: Welcome home to this modern 3 bedroom home constructed in 2021. This 2-story home offers a spacious open living area with a kitchen adorned by a stylish island that invites gatherings and entertainment. The home also features an oversized primary bedroom and ensuite perfect for relaxation. Enjoy the lakeview and community amenities just steps away from your door.
